Feature: deletemessage
	In order to delete sent messages
	As an admin or employee
	I click on delete message

Scenario: try deleting a message as admin
	Given I am logged in as admin
	And I am on send message page
	When I click on "Delete message"
	Then I should see "Message removed"
Scenario: try deleting a message as employee
	Given I am logged in as employee
	And I am on send message page
	When I click on "Delete message"
	Then I should see "Message removed"